ns5:Work.dc:title: Clock without frame
ns5:Work.dc:description: A remix of Clock With Wood Frame by rg1024. I loved the face, but didn't like the frame, so I deleted it. I also rigged the hands for easy rotation. Just download as SVG and edit in software like Ink Scape. Open the layers, turn off the glass, select the hands by clicking twice and rotate to the time you want.
